  <brief_title>Exercise in Patients With a Biventricular Pacemaker</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of an Exercise Program on the Tendance to Severe Arrhythmias in Patients With Severely Impaired Left Ventricular Function and Cardial Re-synchronisation Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
