  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will evaluate the effects of an exercise program (walking on a treadmill)
      on the physical performance, the cardiorespiratory function, the proclivity to heart
      arrhythmias and the quality of life of patients with severely impaired left ventricular
      function and a bi-ventricular resynchronization pacemaker.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
